ledgersmb-1.7 (1.7.0-1~1) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Initial v1.7 upstream release.
  * Change the perl minimum version dependancy to '5.18.0' in debian/control.
  * Update for new v1.7 upstream: debian/control, debian/copyright, debian/rules,
    debian/templates, debian/watch, debian/patches/*.
  * Add 'libtest2-suite-perl' to Build-Depends-Indep in debian/control.
  * Add 'libexcel-writer-xlsx-perl' to the dependencies in debian/control.
  * Add 'libopenoffice-oodoc-perl' to the dependencies in debian/control.
  * Create and update debian/ledgersmb-1.7.* files as necessary for new upstream.

